{
  "texts": [
    "The progressive growing training of StyleGAN starts with a low resolution and gradually increases the resolution of generated images during training.",
    "This approach helps stabilize the training process and allows the generator to focus on generating coarse details first before adding finer details, resulting in more coherent and realistic images.",
    "StyleGAN is known for its ability to generate diverse and unique images from the same latent code.",
    "By controlling the style and structure separately, it allows for the manipulation of individual aspects of the generated image, such as changing the pose, color, and facial expressions while keeping the underlying structure consistent (Saxena and Cao 2021).",
    "The variants of GANs, such as vanilla GAN, DCGAN, CGAN, and WGAN, are limited to the generation of a single image domain using latent input z."
  ]
}